# PromptEnhance Environment Variables

## ---- Optional ---- 

# If not provided, the app will use mock embeddings (works fine for testing)
# Get your API key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Override the default project path
# Default: current working directory
# PROJECT_PATH=/path/to/your/project

# Option 1: Local ChromaDB Server (runs in-memory by default)
# CHROMA_SERVER_URL=http://localhost:8000


--------


# Option 2: ChromaDB Cloud (Recommended for production)
# Get your credentials from: https://trychroma.com/signup
# Note: For CloudClient, CHROMA_SERVER_URL is not needed (defaults to api.trychroma.com)
# CHROMA_API_KEY=ck-your-api-key-here
# CHROMA_TENANT=your-tenant-id
# CHROMA_DATABASE=your-database-name